kumasi   ( historically spelled kumase or coomassie ) kumasi metropolis,coomassie and magdala the story of two british campaigns in africa is a metropolis in ghana and is the capital city of ashanti situated on the semi - island exclave ashantiland .

a cup of kofi : the first u.n. head from africa south of the sahara , kofi annan was born in the city of kumasi in this country in 1938

